des:
C&JsmartFIRE app help you control home appliance. You can simply ask Alexa to control your fireplace. There's no need to go to the switch to adjust your fireplace - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo. After connecting Alexa to your fireplace in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our C&JsmartFIRE app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure your fireplace in our C&JsmartFIRE app and change appropriate name for your firepalce;
(3) Enable C&JsmartFIRE skill, and you'll be navigated to C&JsmartFIRE login page;
(4) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(5) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the living room fireplace.
Alexa, turn off the living room fireplace.
Alexa, turn on flames on the living room fireplace.
Alexa, turn off heat on the living room fireplace.
Alexa, set the living room fireplace to 50%.
Alexa, set the living room fireplace flame color to color one.
